Transcription.Text: The merest glimpse of a man's face is sufficient warning to the initiated, but I have no proof. Therefore be on your guard. "Now for youre instructions." Snatch a moment when the house is unoccupied - but don't send the servants out too obviously - then go upstairs to the attic.
